  "prompt": "Do guys friendzone you because they dont want to lose you?",
  "response": "Friend zoning can happen for various reasons, and one common reason some guys might do it is indeed to maintain a relationship without risking the potential loss that can come with a romantic endeavor. They may value your friendship highly and fear that pursuing a romantic relationship could jeopardize that bond if things don\u2019t work out. Additionally, they might not feel a romantic spark or may be dealing with their own personal issues that prevent them from wanting a relationship.\n\nUltimately, motivations vary from person to person, and it\u2019s important to communicate openly about feelings and intentions if you're seeking clarity in a relationship.",
